description: Try our easy to follow Dim Sim & Veggie Soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Soup,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Nov 2019,High protein,Dinner Made Easy,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Dim Sim & Veggie Soup Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat stock and 2 cups water in a medium saucepan over medium-high heat until simmering. Add hoisin and stir until dissolved.
Add dim sims to pan and cook for 15 minutes, stirring to prevent them sinking to the bottom of the pan, or until cooked through.
Add vegetables to pan and cook for a further 1 minute or until heated through.
Ladle into serving bowls and serve.
